{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.45","c":"وَالْعَادِيَاتِ","d":"wal-ʿādiyāti","e":"ِtَٰyِdَٰʿعْlٱَw"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.19","c":"ضَبْحًا","d":"ḍabḥan","e":"āًḥْbَḍ"}],"a":{"g":"By the racers, panting,"}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.5","c":"فَالْمُورِيَاتِ","d":"fal-mūriyāti","e":"ِtَٰyِrwُmْlٱَf"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.18","c":"قَدْحًا","d":"qadḥan","e":"āًḥْdَq"}],"a":{"g":"And the producers of sparks [when] striking"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"فَالْمُغِيرَاتِ","d":"fal-mughīrāti","e":"ِtَٰryِغُmْlٱَf"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.92","c":"صُبْحًا","d":"ṣub'ḥan","e":"āًḥْbُṣ"}],"a":{"g":"And the chargers at dawn,"}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"فَأَثَرْنَ","d":"fa-atharna","e":"َnْrَhtَaʾَf"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.97","c":"بِهِ","d":"bihi","e":"ۦِhِb"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.13","c":"نَقْعًا","d":"naqʿan","e":"āًʿعْqَn"}],"a":{"g":"Stirring up thereby [clouds of] dust,","ihya":"<div class='ihya-container' style='margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #d4af37; border-radius: 4px;'><h4 style='color: #d4af37; margin-bottom: 15px; font-family: \"Cinzel\", serif;'>Ihya 'Ulum al-Din Commentary</h4><div class='ihya-entry'><span class='badge badge-light' style='color: #666; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin-bottom: 8px;'>Vol1 book 8</span><div class='ihya-text' style='font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;'>Indeed, ambiguity may also occur in the letters, such as the saying of the Almighty, the Exalted: \"So they stirred up thereby a cloud [of dust], and they stormed thereby into the assembly [fa-atharna bihi naq'an fa-wasatna bihi jam'an].\" The first 'him' [bihi] is a metaphor for the hooves, which are the igniters [al-mūriyāt], meaning they stirred up a cloud [of dust] with the hooves. And the second 'him' [bihi] is a metaphor for the raid, which are the raiders at dawn [al-mughīrāt ṣubḥan], so they stormed with it into the assembly, the assembly of the polytheists, and they raided with their assembly.</div></div></div>"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.35","c":"فَوَسَطْنَ","d":"fawasaṭna","e":"َnْṭَsَwَf"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.97","c":"بِهِ","d":"bihi","e":"ۦِhِb"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.11","c":"جَمْعًا","d":"jamʿan","e":"āًʿعْmَjg"}],"a":{"g":"Arriving thereby in the center collectively,"}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"َّnِiʾ"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.92","c":"الْإِنْسَانَ","d":"l-insāna","e":"َnَٰsnِiʾْlٱ"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.51","c":"لِرَبِّهِ","d":"lirabbihi","e":"ۦِhِّbَrِl"},{"b":"4.7","h":"6.7","c":"لَكَنُودٌ","d":"lakanūdun","e":"ٌdwُnَkَl"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed mankind, to his Lord, is ungrateful."}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.45","c":"وَإِنَّهُ","d":"wa-innahu","e":"ۥُhَّnِiʾَw"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.52","c":"عَلَى","d":"ʿalā","e":"ٰàَlَʿع"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.56","c":"ذَلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"َkِlَٰhd"},{"b":"3.5","h":"5.14","c":"لَشَهِيدٌ","d":"lashahīdun","e":"ٌdyِhَhsَl"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed, he is to that a witness."}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.51","c":"وَإِنَّهُ","d":"wa-innahu","e":"ۥُhَّnِiʾَw"},{"b":"2.0","h":"2.73","c":"لِحُبِّ","d":"liḥubbi","e":"ِّbُḥِl"},{"b":"2.9","h":"4.06","c":"الْخَيْرِ","d":"l-khayri","e":"ِrْyَhkْlٱ"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.51","c":"لَشَدِيدٌ","d":"lashadīdun","e":"ٌdyِdَhsَl"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed he is, in love of wealth, intense."}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.5","c":"أَفَلَا","d":"afalā","e":"āَlَfَaʾ"},{"b":"0.88","h":"1.7","c":"يَعْلَمُ","d":"yaʿlamu","e":"ُmَlْʿعَy"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.11","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"āَhdِiʾ"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.18","c":"بُعْثِرَ","d":"buʿ'thira","e":"َrِhtْʿعُb"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.59","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"āَm"},{"b":"3.7","h":"6.34","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"àِf"},{"b":"3.9","h":"6.75","c":"الْقُبُورِ","d":"l-qubūri","e":"ِrwُbُqْlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"But does he not know that when the contents of the graves are scattered"}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.36","c":"وَحُصِّلَ","d":"waḥuṣṣila","e":"َlِّṣُḥَw"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.96","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"āَm"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.7","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"àِf"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.08","c":"الصُّدُورِ","d":"l-ṣudūri","e":"ِrwُdُّṣlٱ"}],"a":{"g":"And that within the breasts is obtained,"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"َّnِiʾ"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.76","c":"رَبَّهُمْ","d":"rabbahum","e":"mُhَّbَr"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4","c":"بِهِمْ","d":"bihim","e":"ْmِhِb"},{"b":"3.8","h":"4.98","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"yawma-idhin","e":"ٍhdِyʾَmْwَy"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.87","c":"لَخَبِيرٌ","d":"lakhabīrun","e":"ٌۢryِbَhkَّl"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, their Lord with them, that Day, is [fully] Acquainted."}}}